---
import BaseLayout from '@/components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import HowIWorkLoop from '@/components/diagrams/HowIWorkLoop.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Qadan"
  description="Moe Qadan. UX and frontend systems, working at the intersection of UX and platform-scale engineering."
>
  <div class="about">
    <div class="about__hero">
      <div class="container-site">
        <span class="about__eyebrow">About</span>
        <h1 class="about__title">
          How I <em>work</em>.
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-site about__body">
      <div class="about__prose">
        <p class="about__lead">
          Most of my work isn't about building from scratch. It's about
          stepping into what already exists and making it better.
        </p>

        <p class="about__para">
          That means:
        </p>

        <ul class="about__bullets">
          <li>Understanding constraints before changing anything</li>
          <li>Improving structure instead of adding complexity</li>
          <li>Building things that can be reused, not just shipped</li>
          <li>Knowing when to automate and when not to</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="about__para">
          <strong>AI is part of how I build now.</strong> It's part of
          the stack, like everything else I use. I treat it the way I'd
          treat any other tool with real surface area: structured inputs,
          constrained outputs, deliberate iteration. The model drafts,
          refactors, and handles the parts that compound over time. I
          keep the architecture, the decisions, and the review.
        </p>

        <p class="about__para">
          I also run small agents inside the workflow. Short-lived, scoped
          to one job, used where it makes sense. Just another tool in
          the build, sitting alongside the rest of the stack. They don't
          replace the work. They make the work move.
        </p>

        <p class="about__para">
          The goal is always the same: make the hard parts easier to use,
          and cheaper to evolve.
        </p>

        <HowIWorkLoop />

        <hr class="about__rule" />

        <h2 class="about__h2">A few things that shape the work</h2>

        <ol class="about__list">
          <li>
            <strong>Systems before surfaces.</strong> A page is a render of
            something deeper. Get the underlying structure right and the
            surface gets cheaper to change.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Constraints are the brief.</strong> A long-running
            platform, a legacy stack, a business that depends on what's
            already running. Those aren't obstacles. They're the actual
            design problem.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>AI runs through the workflow now.</strong> Agentic
            workflows, structured prompts, AI-assisted development. Used
            in the parts where it earns its keep.
          </li>
        </ol>

        <p class="about__signature">
          Most systems don't need to be replaced. They need to be
          understood first.
        </p>

        <hr class="about__rule" />

        <h2 class="about__h2">The kind of work I take on</h2>

        <div class="about__columns">
          <div class="about__col">
            <span class="about__col-label about__col-label--yes">
              <span class="about__col-mark" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
              Interested in
            </span>
            <ul class="about__col-list">
              <li>Long-running platforms with real constraints</li>
              <li>AI-native products where structure beats vibes</li>
              <li>System-level UX, not single-page polish</li>
              <li>Frontend architecture in environments that can't be torn down</li>
              <li>Tooling and workflows where AI is the delivery layer, not the demo</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="about__col">
            <span class="about__col-label about__col-label--no">
              <span class="about__col-mark" aria-hidden="true">−</span>
              Less interested in
            </span>
            <ul class="about__col-list">
              <li>Greenfield-from-greenfield with no domain</li>
              <li>"AI feature for AI feature's sake" projects</li>
              <li>Visual refresh without structural change</li>
              <li>Agency-style throughput across many shallow surfaces</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="about__aside">
        <div class="about__card">
          <h3 class="about__card-title">Currently</h3>
          <ul class="about__card-list">
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Platform</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">MagTek &amp; related sites</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Product</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">ChatOBD2</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Stack</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">ASP.NET MVC · Razor · C# · TypeScript · React · Astro</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="about__card-key">Workflow</span>
              <span class="about__card-val">Cursor + Claude · agentic loops</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about__card">
          <h3 class="about__card-title">Reach out</h3>
          <p class="about__card-note">
            Open to interesting work: products, platforms, AI-native
            systems.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="about__card-cta">
            Get in touch
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about__hero {
    padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-16));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .about__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 18ch;
  }

  .about__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
  }

  .about__lead {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 56ch;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about__para {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .about__columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  .about__col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
  }

  .about__col-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about__col-mark {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about__col-label--yes .about__col-mark {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent-muted);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
  }

  .about__col-label--no .about__col-mark {
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
  }

  .about__col-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about__col-list li {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .about__col-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .about__col-label--no ~ .about__col-list li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .about__signature {
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .about__bullets {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__bullets li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .about__bullets li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.7em;
    width: 12px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about__rule {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: var(--space-10) 0;
  }

  .about__h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 30px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about__list {
    counter-reset: about-list;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about__list li {
    counter-increment: about-list;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 36px;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about__list li::before {
    content: counter(about-list, decimal-leading-zero);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .about__list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about__aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__card {
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
  }

  .about__card-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__card-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .about__card-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .about__card-key {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .about__card-val {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .about__card-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about__card-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 150ms, border-color 150ms;
  }

  .about__card-cta:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
